#: ../../SO5.md:680
msgid "The suggested approach is to draw upon the OECD DAC CRS database for ODA flows, OOF, and Private development finance and the Rio Marker for desertification, and select projects specifically aimed at transferring or developing technologies to combat DLDD or with a relevant component. It is possible to consider resources extended to teaching institutions, research institutes and similar agencies. There are potential interlinkages with projects dealing with technologies for climate adaptation, for which taxonomies and classifications are available[^6],  which could serve as a reference for the identification of relevant technologies."
